snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio "Bharat" is perhaps the most disappointing edition of All Coke Studio seasons across nations. The artists are mediocre. The lyrics are balderdash. The instruments are mechanized trash. It makes bollywood sound like a good promoter of classical music. Please look up to the past Coke Studio seasons, especially those of Pakistan and Bangladesh to understand how to curate good music and popularize traditional art forms while maintaining authenticity. Also, check out the Lahooti project. This is just bad. Had such great expectations.
snippet.textOriginal: Coke Studio "Bharat" is perhaps the most disappointing edition of All Coke Studio seasons across nations. The artists are mediocre. The lyrics are balderdash. The instruments are mechanized trash. It makes bollywood sound like a good promoter of classical music. Please look up to the past Coke Studio seasons, especially those of Pakistan and Bangladesh to understand how to curate good music and popularize traditional art forms while maintaining authenticity. Also, check out the Lahooti project. This is just bad. Had such great expectations.
